Brand new video for 'Brains'. Track produced by Illinformed, cuts by DJ Sammy B-Side. This is the second single to be released from Jam Baxter's new project 'The Gruesome Features' which is out early July on High Focus Records on CD, Digital & Limited Edition EP version on vinyl. The Brains single comes with the instrumental included.

Video Credits:
Produced by Jam Baxter
Directed by Harry Wheeler
Edited by Andrew Hugh Craig
Costume by Jenna at Prangsta
